Data Subscriptions

Explore Seamless Data Subscriptions.

Our Data Subscription feature allows you to effortlessly purchase data plans directly through the Paysusofi app. Experience convenience, speed, and control over your data usage like never before.

How It Works

Discover the simplicity of Paysusofi’s seamless process.

Select Mobile Carrier

Choose your network provider from a list of supported options. Paysusofi caters to various networks, ensuring compatibility with your preferred service provider.

Select Your Plan

Choose from a variety of data plans that suit your needs. Whether it's daily, weekly, or monthly, Paysusofi offers flexibility in selecting the right plan for you.

Review and Confirm

Easily fund your Paysusofi account. Add funds with the payment method of your choice, ensuring your wallet is ready for transactions.

Instant Activation

Enjoy instant activation of your chosen data plan. No delays – your data subscription is ready to use right when you need it.
